title: Bobby Reveals The TV Show He’s Going To Be On + Listener Tries To Win Bobby’s Money

description:
Bobby finally hit 1 million followers on Instagram. As promised, he reveals the TV show he’s going to be on soon. Producer Raymundo hosts today’s “Win Bobby’s Money” trivia game. Also, the show debates if Amy’s husband saved a life as a lifeguard.
